xtc.lang
Class JavaNoSourceAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
  xtc.lang.JavaNoSourceAnalyzer

public final class JavaNoSourceAnalyzer
extends Object

Uses reflection to construct externally visible types and fill in the symbol table for entities for which no source code is available. This is not a visitor, but has similar method names to emphasize the similarities with JavaExternalAnalyzer.
